        <div class="msgSubject">GuildFans: Exclusive Interview With Eric Flannum!</div>
        <div class="sm notbold">
          
          Posted: 2010-11-17 06:06:51 | Edited: Nov 19 2010 11:33am  | <input type="checkbox" name="quote-1289995611260193255" id="quote-1289995611260193255" class="msgQuoteCheck" onchange="multiQuote2()"/><label for="quote-1289995611260193255" onclick="multiQuote2()"> Quote</label>  | <a href="/forum.html?forum=226&amp;mid=1289995611260193255&amp;post=1&amp;replyto=1289995611260193255&amp;page=1" class="icon-replytothis" rel="nofollow">Reply to Post</a> | <a id="FOLLOW_MID_1289995611260193255" onclick="followToggle('add','1289995611260193255')" href="javascript:" class="icon-follow">Follow</a> 
