      <div class="msgContentFrame">I liked everything concerning stealth except for &quot;stealth detection skills.&quot; The moment I feel the need to swap out one of my other utility skills for a stealth detection skill, I'll really be upset. Stealth should be something that will provide a slight advantage to professions that use it if someone isn't paying attention - exactly how stealth works IRL. I don't want to have to &quot;need&quot; to have a skill to detect someone stealthing. </div>
